All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
CovidTracker
The CovidTrakcer is a Display that keeps track of the number of Covid cases in each Tier
Display
The Display class represents an object that is displayed on the window
Doctor
The Doctor class represents a Person that is immune to Covid and can be used to create Hospitals.
DrawingSurface
The DrawingSurface class draws the components of program on the window and updates them based on user actions
Factory
The Factory class represents a Place that makes masks.
GameComponent
Represents a component on the grid of a Tier
Hospital
The Hospital class represents a Place that cures the infected people and can hold 5 patients at a time.
Inventory
The Inventory class is a Display that shows what the player has
Location
Represents the location of a person in the Tier
Main
The Main class represents the start of entire program
Map
The Map class is a Display which represents the map of California and boxes which are both interactive.
Menu
The Menu class is a Display that represents the options that the user has regarding the program
OrangeTier
Represents the second level Tier, or the Orange Tier.
Person
This class represents a Person on the grid displayed in a Tier
Place
This class represents a private place on the grid displayed in a Tier
Player
The Player class is a Person that is controlled by the user.
PublicPlace
A type of Place, a public place can be converted into hospital in certain conditions
PurpleTier
Represents the fourth level Tier, or the Purple Tier.
RedTier
The RedTier class represents a Tier which is level 3.
Researcher
A Researcher is an invincible person, who can open up vaccine clinics
TaskBar
The TaskBar class represents a Display that gives the user recommended tasks to complete in each Tier.
Tier
This class represents the overall structure of a Tier, or level, in the Mask On! game
TimerDisplay
The TimerDisplay class is a Display that represents a stopwatch used to keep track of how much time the user spends on a Tier
VaccineClinic
The VaccineClinic represents a Place that vaccinates people.
YellowTier
Represents the first level Tier, or the Yellow Tier.
